Commentary: The Hopi Chiefs believe that at this time all the remaining
  "spiritual threads" of the World are looking lo each other for help and
  encouragement, for many threads make a rope which shall lead out of this
  cycle and into the next. (Joseph Epes Brown, in a letter).
